<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,500" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Oswald:300,400,500,700" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body>
  <table class="mail">
    <thead>
      <tr style="height: 35px;"></tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="min-width: 58px;"></th>
        <th class="mail__header-width">
          <h1 class="mail__title">Save encerrado estamos quase lá!</h1>
        </th>
        <th style="min-width: 58px;"></th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="min-width: 58px;"></th>
        <th class="mail__header-width">
          <p class="mail__subtitle">
            O Save de {{ save.title }} já está encerrado e os fabricantes estão nos enviando suas ofertas.
            <br/>
            Estamos avaliando e em breve disponibilizaremos as melhores para votação.
          </p>
        </th>
        <th style="min-width: 58px;"></th>
      </tr>
      <tr style="height: 25px;"></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td style="min-width: 28px;"></td>
        <td class="mail__content-wrapper">
          <table class="mail__content">
            <tbody>
              <tr style="height: 21px;"></tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <img class="product__image" src="{{ save.image_default }}" alt="{{ save.title }}">
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p class="small_text">Imagem meramente ilustrativa</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <h1 class="heading">{{ save.title }}</h1>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p class="description">{{ save.description }}</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="height: 18px;"></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </td>
        <td style="min-width: 28px;"></td>
      </tr>
      {{> mail-footer}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <style>
    .mail {
      width: 100%;
      background: #1d2028;
    }

    .mail__header-width {
      width: 600px;
    }

    .mail__title {
      text-align: left;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.47;
      color: #fff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .mail__subtitle {
      text-align: left;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #fff;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .heading {
      color: #FFF;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
      font-size: '26px';
      font-weight: '500';
      margin: 0;
    }

    .small_text {
      text-align: center;
      color: #FFF;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      font-size: 8px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .description {
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
      color: #acb2c0;
      display: -webkit-box;
      height: 50px;
      overflow: hidden;
      -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
      -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
      font-family: "Oswald", sans-serif;
    }

    .mail__product-wrapper {
      width: 600px;
      border: 1px solid #253e4f;
    }

    .product__logo-wrapper {
      height: 57px;
      width: 57px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .product__logo {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .product__text {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #acb2c0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .product__text--label {
      width: 194px;
      color: #1d2028;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .product__text--method {
      font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .product__text--label-buscape {
      color: #1d2028;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .product__text--date-buscape {
      font-size: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .product__title {
      text-align: left;
      font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #fff;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .product__image {
      height: 250px;
    }

    .product__price {
      text-align: left;
      font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1d2028;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .product__price--buscape {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .product__button,
    .product__button:visited,
    .product__button:focus {
      display: block;
      width: 250px;
      height: 44px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 44px;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 2px;
      background-color: #28ba64;
      box-shadow: inset 0 -2px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .product__buscape-container {
      background: #f1f1f1;
    }

    .mail__content-wrapper {
      width: 600px;
    }

    .mail__content {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 2px;
      color: #FFF;
    }
  </style>
</body>

</html>
